Ladhe Wala Waraich (Punjabi and }}), is a city of Gujranwala District in the Punjab province of Pakistan. The city is part Gujranwala Saddar Tehsil. Ladhe Wala Waraich lies to the west of Gujranwala and is part of the larger metropolitan area.
